[Nouns] orange, red and yellow; gold; or; flame color.
[Pigments] ocher, Mars' orange, cadmium.
cardinal bird, cardinal flower, cardinal grosbeak, cardinal lobelia.
[Verbs] gild, warm.
[Adjectives] orange; ochreous; orange-colored, gold-colored, flame-colored, copper-colored, brass-colored, apricot-colored; warm, hot, glowing.
